data.description: Are you looking for all the bells and whistles?  Look no further! This beautiful 4-bedroom 2 bath home is what you are looking for. Home features an open floor plan, granite counter tops, custom black splash, ceramic floors throughout the, living, kitchen, and bathrooms. Just to add a little more excitement home also features a custom fireplace and a HUGE oversized back yard along with a perfect nook office area to work from home and so much more!
